section: ==The Farewell Party Band==.  In 2022, Gene Watson celebrates his 60th Anniversary in the music business which started with his independent release "If It's That Easy".  The 45 single shows the label as Sun Valley Records. When asked about that label, Gene admitted that "Sun Valley" was simply the name of the street where the drummer lived. He was not signed to any label at that time.
